01:07:03.719 --> 01:07:09.879
usage and compute time by up to 10 acts compared to pandas, the standard, well, or at least

01:07:09.879 --> 01:07:15.399
until recently until bullies came along the standard dataframe operations library.

01:07:15.399 --> 01:07:20.520
Poller uses a grammar where expressions function like recipes, operations are steps and functions

01:07:20.520 --> 01:07:26.479
or methods are the cooks creating readable code without excessive brackets.

01:07:26.479 --> 01:07:30.760
We talked about how when implemented at alley under a Dutch power grid provider, pollers

01:07:30.760 --> 01:07:35.479
reduced memory requirements from 500 gigabytes to 40 gigabytes.

01:07:35.479 --> 01:07:39.760
So a 10 X reduction and doubled processing capacity.

